    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound BMW E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing. This driver-focused example delivers a linear power band and a soaring 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. Key preventative maintenance includes a reinforced rear subframe and rod bearing service, ensuring structural integrity under high lateral loads. The suspension geometry remains tight with refreshed bushings, offering the precise turn-in and feedback expected of the M-chassis. A visceral, analog performance machine ready for the tarmac.",
